					<div class="block" id="b1">
						<h4>Property services</h4>
						<p>Totally scaleable, Optima Legal offer a full legal service solution from HIPs through to residential recoveries. This unique and innovative approach provides our clients with complete peace of mind as we understand every step of the customer lifecycle.</p>
						<p>Our integrated solution significantly reduces case management administration and duplication allowing clients to benefit from a better return on investment and quicker turnaround times. </p>
						
					</div>
					<div class="block" id="b2">
						<h4>Other asset based services </h4>
				
						<p>Through a combination of highly experienced negotiators, legal techniques and a first class IT infrastructure, our innovative legal solutions are designed to quickly and effectively rehabilitate and recover the asset from the debtor. We act for many of the UK's top asset finance businesses who trust us to identify their issues and provide a solution tailored to meet their requirements.</p> 
						
						<p>Regardless of whether the service needed is for the return of goods or factoring and invoice discount collections, Optima Legal have a comprehensive solution that covers all of England, Wales and Scotland.</p> 
						
					</div>
					<div class="block" id="b3">
						<h4>Unsecured lender services </h4>
					
						<p>Optima Legal offer a range of innovative services designed to recover outstanding monetary amounts owed by customers on your behalf. Our expertise and experience with banks and credit card providers means that we can offer a cost effective, transparent and bespoke solution to suit your individual requirements.</p>
						
					</div>
					<div class="block" id="b4">
						<h4>Non-lender Services</h4>
						<p>Optima Legal act for a range of clients from diverse market sectors including Utilities, Telecommunications, Hotels, Recruitment, Education, Retail, and Estate Agencies.  Through our experience, legal heritage and innovative approach, our mission is to maximise your commercial results whilst preserving important existing customer relationships.</p>
						
					</div>
